                        <p class="text-gray-400">Showcase your bots to a growing community of Discord users. Get valuable feedback and increase your bot's visibility.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6 bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl border border-gray-700/50">
